OL,3,C'Lonely and rough': 23-year-old sofa-
OL,4,Csurfer on hidden homelessness in NI
OL,6,FThe number of people who are
OL,7,Fconsidered homeless in Northern
OL,8,FIreland could be 25,000 higher than
OL,9,Fthe government's count, according to
OL,10,Fthe Simon Community.
OL,12,FThe charity has revealed research
OL,13,Festimating that the true figure in NI
OL,14,Fis 80,000, with the disparity in
OL,15,Fnumbers being due to the fact that
OL,16,Fmany people are experiencing "hidden
OL,17,Fhomelessness".
OL,19,FThis figure is around the same as the
OL,20,Fentire population of Derry city.
