OL,3,C'Lonely and rough': 23-year-old sofa-
OL,4,Csurfer on hidden homelessness in NI
OL,6,FThe Fermanagh man had been
OL,7,Fexperiencing drink and drug problems
OL,8,Fwhen he had a family fall out, and
OL,9,Fthen spent months not knowing where he
OL,10,Fwould sleep the next night.
OL,12,FJustin said he moved to Belfast where
OL,13,Fhe was often supported by another
OL,14,Ffamily member, but that they did not
OL,15,Falways have space for him.
OL,17,FSo, he would wander around, drifting
OL,18,Finto parties so that he would have a
OL,19,Fplace to be, which meant that his
OL,20,Frelationship with illicit substances
OL,21,Fwent from bad to worse.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
