OL,6,F"It was hard, it made my mental health
OL,7,Fnot good. You don't know if you're
OL,8,Fgoing to have a bed to sleep in," he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"I never thought I would become
OL,12,Fhomeless, I always felt secure and
OL,13,Fsafe growing up so it just shows you,
OL,14,Fit can happen to anyone."
OL,16,FHe said accessing a Simon Community
OL,17,Fhostel has been life changing, even
OL,18,Ffrom a health perspective.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
