OL,6,F"The Simon Community has got me a GP,
OL,7,FI haven't had a GP in five or six
OL,8,Fyears so I'm finally going to be able
OL,9,Fto get my head sorted and get off
OL,10,Fsubstances."
OL,12,FHe said he hopes then to get a job in
OL,13,Fa shop, and then meet someone and get
OL,14,Fmarried and have a family.
OL,16,FA total of 46,000 people are waiting
OL,17,Ffor social housing in Northern
OL,18,FIreland, and every year the NI Housing
OL,19,FExecutive sells around 500 homes
OL,20,Fthrough help to buy.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
