OL,6,FIt means that an announcement last
OL,7,Fweek of 400 new social homes is "a
OL,8,Fdrop in the ocean", according to the
OL,9,FSimon Community.
OL,11,FMeanwhile the private housing market
OL,12,Fis also under huge pressure, with the
OL,13,Faverage rental price in Belfast
OL,14,Fsitting at over #900.
OL,16,F"We are in Northern Ireland in a
OL,17,Fhousing and homelessness crisis," said
OL,18,FKirsten Hewitt from the charity.
OL,20,F"It's even worse than we thought," she
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
