OL,6,F"We need to focus on prevention, to
OL,7,Fstop people from becoming homeless,
OL,8,Fand then focus on the individuals in
OL,9,Fthe system."
OL,11,FThe figures were presented to dozens
OL,12,Fof people at Clifton House. They
OL,13,Fincluded reps from the Department for
OL,14,FCommunities, the Department of Health,
OL,15,Fhealth trusts, Belfast City Council,
OL,16,FNICCY, the Housing Executive, QUB and
OL,17,FUlster University, reflecting how the
OL,18,Fproblem draws in many departments.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
