OL,6,FIn a statement, the Department for
OL,7,FCommunities said: "The Minister has
OL,8,Foutlined his ambition to prioritise
OL,9,Fprevention of homelessness, working
OL,10,Fwith the NIHE and the sector to ensure
OL,11,Fthat homelessness is rare, brief and
OL,12,Fnon-recurrent.
OL,14,F"The Minister recognises that it will
OL,15,Ftake time ` and a collective effort `
OL,16,Fto achieve this ambition, particularly
OL,17,Fgiven the ongoing cost of providing
OL,18,Ftemporary accommodation, which is
OL,19,Fincreasing for a range of reasons.
