OL,6,F"However, the short-term focus must
OL,7,Fcontinue to be supporting those
OL,8,Fcurrently in crisis.
OL,10,F"Alongside this, the Department has
OL,11,Ftaken forward a broad range of
OL,12,Finitiatives to address the wider issue
OL,13,Fof housing provision and need. This
OL,14,Fwork is ongoing with stakeholders,
OL,15,Fstatutory organisations and residents,
OL,16,Fwith the involvement of government at
OL,17,Fall levels."
