OL,6,FThe statement continued that the
OL,7,FMinister "has also outlined his
OL,8,Fdisappointment" that the capital
OL,9,Ffunding does not exist to build more
OL,10,Fsocial homes.
OL,12,F"As work continues to protect the
OL,13,Frange of essential services within the
OL,14,FDepartment's remit, the Minister will
OL,15,Fcontinue to make the case for more
OL,16,Ffunding to address the growing housing
OL,17,Fneed.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
