OL,6,F"Alongside this, targeted engagement
OL,7,Fis ongoing to consider the impact for
OL,8,Fthe housing association sector and to
OL,9,Fdiscuss a range of housing issues.
OL,11,F"The consultation on proposed DfC
OL,12,Fbudget allocations opens this week and
OL,13,Fthe Department will engage directly
OL,14,Fwith key stakeholders.
OL,16,F"All responses will feed into the
OL,17,Fdecision making process going forward,
OL,18,Fand help to shape the broad range of
OL,19,Fpublic services which the Department
OL,20,Fdelivers."
